race.description: North Ryde Rsl Moruya Showcase Cup Handicap
race.comment: ARTFUL PERSUASION (8) is going better than his form suggests on paper. Chipped away late from the awkward gate when seventh to the progressive The Mona Lisa over the mile at Randwick and beaten 3.5 lengths. Proven at the trip and will relish the fast tempo. DUMEBI (9) justified the good support into favouritism at his second run back when a tenacious nose winner over 1300m at this track. Meeting a tougher field but has the upside to go on with it now. GENETIC FREAK (5) returned from a let-up with a fading tenth over 1300m at this track with the 57kg. Drops sharply in weight with Baker's 3kg claim and can run into the minor money. SUPER EXTREME (10) came from last on the turn when a slashing fifth over the 1300m in the Narooma Cup at this track. Gets map favours today and shapes as a solid value chance. The race doesn't end there.
